awesomeListRepo":"Urigo/awesome-meteor","categoryHTML":"<h2>Work Opportunities</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://jobs.meteor.com/\">Official Job Board</a></li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T19:02:36.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"dariubs/GoBooks","categoryHTML":"<h2><strong>Starter Books</strong></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://go101.org/article/101.html\">Go 101</a> <em>Free</em></h3>\n<img src=\"https://go101.org/article/res/101-front-cover-1400x.jpg\" width=\"120px\">\n<p>Go 101 is a book focusing on Go syntax/semantics and all kinds of runtime related things (Go 1.17-pre ready) and tries to help gophers gain a deep and thorough understanding of Go. This book also collects many details of Go and in Go programming. It is expected that this book is helpful for both beginner and experienced Go programmers.</p>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T18:50:25.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"dariubs/GoBooks","categoryHTML":"<h2><strong>Advanced Books</strong></h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://www.packtpub.com/product/security-with-go/9781788627917\">Security with Go</a></h3>\n<img src=\"https://static.packt-cdn.com/products/9781788627917/cover/smaller\" width=\"120px\">\n<p>Security with Go is the first Golang security book, and it is useful for both blue team and red team applications. With this book, you will learn how to write secure software, monitor your systems, secure your data, attack systems, and extract information.</p>\n<p>Defensive topics include cryptography, forensics, packet capturing, and building secure web applications.</p>\n<p>Offensive topics include brute force, port scanning, packet injection, web scraping, social engineering, and post exploitation techniques.</p>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T18:50:25.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DanailMinchev/awesome-eosio","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Websites</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://developers.eos.io/\">EOSIO Developer Portal</a> - A great place to begin your EOSIO blockchain journey.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T17:10:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DanailMinchev/awesome-eosio","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Interactive learning, labs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://battles.eos.io/\">Elemental Battles</a> - Build a blockchain game. Learn EOSIO.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://medium.com/eosio/announcing-elemental-battles-block-ones-3215a8e2cdee\">Announcing Elemental Battles: Block.one's New Tutorial for On-boarding Aspiring Blockchain Developers</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T17:10:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"DanailMinchev/awesome-eosio","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learn</h2><h3>Interactive learning, labs</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://google.qwiklabs.com/catalog_lab/3743\">Block.one: Getting Started with the EOSIO Blockchain and Smart Contracts</a> - Google Cloud training lab.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T17:10:41.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"meirwah/awesome-incident-response","categoryHTML":"<h2>IR tools Collection</h2><h3>Log Analysis Tools</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ahmedkhlief/APT-Hunter\">APT Hunter</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ahmedkhlief/APT-Hunter\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">367</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":367,\"repo\":\"ahmedkhlief/APT-Hunter\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - APT-Hunter is Threat Hunting tool for windows event logs.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-01T17:09:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"meirwah/awesome-incident-response","categoryHTML":"<h2>IR tools Collection<